  "strategy": [
    "Alternate between short forward moves and full scans in clear areas to maximize marker detection.",
    "Switch to marker tracking immediately when marker_seen, prioritizing move_to_marker.",
    "If marker is lost during tracking, perform a full scan to reacquire.",
    "On obstacle detection, use clear recovery steps: move backward or rotate away, followed by a scan.",
    "In obs_left, prefer rotate_clockwise; in obs_right, prefer rotate_counterclockwise to avoid oscillations.",
    "After any forward or recovery action, insert a scan to prevent long straight runs without perception.",
    "When marker_close is detected, transition to a terminal stop state to safely complete the task.",
    "All uncontrollable events are handled in every state to ensure totality and safety."
  ]
